The code requires R > 4.0 and the following packages (version):

sf (1.0-4), gnorm	(1.0.0), mnormt	(2.0.2), rgeos	(0.5-9), raster	(3.5-2), MASS (7.3-54), mvtnorm (1.1-3), matrixStats (0.61.0), metR (0.11.0), data.table (1.14.2), dplyr	(1.0.7), INLA (21.11.22), foreach	(1.5.1), Matrix (1.3-4), inlabru (2.4.0), sp	(1.4-6)